                <h1>Discover Bob Dylan: Music Legend & Icon</h1>
                <p>Bob Dylan, an iconic figure in music, has shaped the landscape of folk and rock since the 1960s. Known for his poetic lyrics and distinct voice, Dylan's work often touches on social issues and personal introspection. His timeless songs like "Blowin' in the Wind" and "Like a Rolling Stone" continue to resonate with generations of fans.</p>
